      <title>java_extends</title>
      <link href="/2021/12/26/java-extends/"/>
      <url>/2021/12/26/java-extends/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="java-继承"><a href="#java-继承" class="headerlink" title="java 继承"></a>java 继承</h1><p><strong>测试类</strong></p><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">package</span> extends_constructor_features<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/** * 子类继承父类后构造器的特点 * 1， */</span><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">test</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">/**    运行结果父类无参构造器被触发++++++++++++++子类无参构造器被触发==============父类有参构造器被触发=============兄弟有参构造器被触发+++++++++++++++朗郁    20    22父类有参构造器被触发=============兄弟有参构造器被触发+++++++++++++++刘洋20格物致知     */</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">static</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> args<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//1，子类中所有的构造器默认都会优先访问父类中的无参构造，在执行自己</span>        Wolf W1 <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">Wolf</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        Wolf W2 <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">Wolf</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"朗郁"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">20</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">"22"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>W2<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">getName</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token string">"\t"</span><span class="token operator">+</span>W2<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">getAge</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">+</span><span class="token string">"\t"</span><span class="token operator">+</span>W2<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">getClassname</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//默认数据初始化例子；</span>        Wolf W3 <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">Wolf</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"刘洋"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">20</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>W3<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">getName</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>W3<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">getAge</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>W3<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">getClassname</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre><p><strong>父类</strong></p><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">package</span> extends_constructor_features<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">animal</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//父类无参构造器</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token function">animal</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"父类无参构造器被触发++++++++++++++"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//父类有参构造器</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token function">animal</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String name<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> age<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"父类有参构造器被触发============="</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>name <span class="token operator">=</span>name<span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>age <span class="token operator">=</span> age<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">private</span> String name<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">private</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> age<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> String <span class="token function">getName</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> name<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">setName</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String name<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>name <span class="token operator">=</span> name<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">getAge</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> age<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">setAge</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">int</span> age<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>age <span class="token operator">=</span> age<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre><p><strong>子类</strong></p><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"><span class="token keyword">package</span> extends_constructor_features<span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">people</span> <span class="token keyword">extends</span>  <span class="token class-name">animal</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>    <span class="token keyword">private</span> String classname<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> String <span class="token function">getClassname</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> classname<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">void</span> <span class="token function">setClassname</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String classname<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>classname <span class="token operator">=</span> classname<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//借用兄弟构造器来简单实现默认数据初始化；</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//此时调用了兄弟构造器，则就不会再去调用父类构造器，</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//因为调用的兄弟构造器中也会去调用父类构造器</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token function">people</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String name<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> age<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>name<span class="token punctuation">,</span>age<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">"格物致知"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token function">people</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//默认第一条语句为</span>        <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//super();</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"子类无参构造器被触发=============="</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>    <span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token function">people</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>String name<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token keyword">int</span> age<span class="token punctuation">,</span> String classname<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>        <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//尽管默认第一条语句为 super();</span>        <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//但是如果手动调用了父类有参构造器，则无参构造器不被触发。</span>        <span class="token keyword">super</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>name<span class="token punctuation">,</span> age<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        System<span class="token punctuation">.</span>out<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">println</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"兄弟有参构造器被触发+++++++++++++++"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>        <span class="token keyword">this</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>classname<span class="token operator">=</span>classname<span class="token punctuation">;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span></code></pre><pre><code></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
